  "ai_usage": "Use as the shell for internal tools / SaaS apps. Copy the document; the layout is a CSS grid (sidebar + topbar + main). Replace nav items, KPI numbers, the bar-chart values (set each bar's height), and the table rows. Wire real data by swapping the static table/chart for components, keeping the grid and tokens. Keep the <table> semantics and add aria labels to charts when populated.",
  "path": "effects/website-templates/admin-dashboard.html",
  "source": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>Admin Dashboard</title>\n  <script type=\"application/json\" id=\"effect-meta\">\n  {\n    \"id\": \"admin-dashboard\",\n    \"title\": \"Admin Dashboard\",\n    \"summary\": \"An app shell: fixed sidebar nav, topbar, KPI stat cards, a pure-CSS bar chart, and a data table.\",\n    \"description\": \"A static dashboard scaffold using the holy-grail grid (sidebar + topbar + content). Includes KPI cards, a CSS-only bar chart placeholder, and a responsive table — the skeleton for an internal tool or SaaS app.\",\n    \"theme\": \"website-templates\",\n    \"categories\": [\"template\", \"dashboard\", \"app\"],\n    \"tags\": [\"dashboard\", \"admin\", \"app-shell\", \"sidebar\", \"table\", \"kpi\", \"full-page\"],\n    \"tech\": [\"css\", \"html\"],\n    \"era\": \"2020s\",\n    \"difficulty\": \"intermediate\",\n    \"dependencies\": [],\n    \"browser_support\": \"All modern browsers (CSS Grid).\",\n    \"performance_notes\": \"No JS or chart library; the bar chart is CSS heights. Swap in a real chart lib when wiring live data.\",\n    \"accessibility_notes\": \"Landmarks (aside/nav/header/main), a real <table> with <th scope>, focus-visible on nav items. Charts need text alternatives when populated with real data.\",\n    \"customization\": [\n      { \"name\": \"--accent / surfaces\", \"description\": \"Brand + panel colors\", \"default\": \"#7c5cff / dark\" },\n      { \"name\": \"grid-template-columns\", \"description\": \"Sidebar width\", \"default\": \"230px 1fr\" }\n    ],\n    \"variations\": [\"Collapsible sidebar (toggle a class)\", \"Light theme\", \"Replace the CSS chart with a real charting lib\"],\n    \"related\": [\"holy-grail\", \"card-lift\", \"skeleton-loader\"],\n    \"ai_usage\": \"Use as the shell for internal tools / SaaS apps. Copy the document; the layout is a CSS grid (sidebar + topbar + main). Replace nav items, KPI numbers, the bar-chart values (set each bar's height), and the table rows. Wire real data by swapping the static table/chart for components, keeping the grid and tokens. Keep the <table> semantics and add aria labels to charts when populated.\"\n  }\n  </script>\n  <style>\n    :root{--bg:#0b0d12;--panel:#11141c;--panel2:#151925;--line:#222838;--text:#e7ebf3;--muted:#8b93a7;--accent:#7c5cff;--accent2:#2dd4bf;}\n    *{box-sizing:border-box;} html,body{margin:0;height:100%;}\n    body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:system-ui,sans-serif;}\n    .app{display:grid;grid-template-columns:220px 1fr;grid-template-rows:56px 1fr;grid-template-areas:\"side top\" \"side main\";height:100vh;}\n    aside{grid-area:side;background:var(--panel);border-right:1px solid var(--line);padding:1rem;}\n    .logo{font-weight:800;margin-bottom:1.4rem;} .logo span{color:var(--accent2);}\n    nav a{display:block;padding:.55rem .7rem;border-radius:8px;color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none;margin-bottom:.2rem;font-size:.92rem;}\n    nav a.active,nav a:hover{background:var(--panel2);color:var(--text);}\n    header{grid-area:top;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:0 1.2rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--panel);}\n    header .search{background:var(--panel2);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:8px;padding:.4rem .8rem;color:var(--muted);font-size:.85rem;width:220px;}\n    .avatar{width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent),var(--accent2));}\n    main{grid-area:main;overflow:auto;padding:1.4rem;}\n    .kpis{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(160px,1fr));gap:1rem;margin-bottom:1.4rem;}\n    .kpi{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:14px;padding:1rem 1.2rem;}\n    .kpi .label{color:var(--muted);font-size:.8rem;} .kpi .num{font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:800;margin:.2rem 0;}\n    .kpi .delta{color:var(--accent2);font-size:.8rem;}\n    .panel{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:14px;padding:1.2rem;margin-bottom:1.4rem;}\n    .panel h3{margin:0 0 1rem;font-size:1rem;}\n    .chart{display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:10px;height:140px;}\n    .chart .bar{flex:1;background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--accent),var(--accent2));border-radius:6px 6px 0 0;}\n    table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:.9rem;}\n    th,td{text-align:left;padding:.6rem .5rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);}\n    th{color:var(--muted);font-weight:600;font-size:.8rem;}\n    .pill{padding:.15rem .55rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.75rem;}\n    .ok{background:rgba(34,197,94,.15);color:#4ade80;} .pend{background:rgba(245,158,11,.15);color:#fbbf24;}\n    @media(max-width:680px){.app{grid-template-columns:1fr;grid-template-areas:\"top\" \"main\";}aside{display:none;}}\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"app\">\n    <aside>\n      <div class=\"logo\">◆ <span>Console</span></div>\n      <nav><a class=\"active\" href=\"#\">Overview</a><a href=\"#\">Customers</a><a href=\"#\">Revenue</a><a href=\"#\">Reports</a><a href=\"#\">Settings</a></nav>\n    </aside>\n    <header><input class=\"search\" placeholder=\"Search…\" /><div class=\"avatar\"></div></header>\n    <main>\n      <div class=\"kpis\">\n        <div class=\"kpi\"><div class=\"label\">MRR</div><div class=\"num\">$48.2k</div><div class=\"delta\">▲ 12.4%</div></div>\n        <div class=\"kpi\"><div class=\"label\">Active users</div><div class=\"num\">9,341</div><div class=\"delta\">▲ 4.1%</div></div>\n        <div class=\"kpi\"><div class=\"label\">Churn</div><div class=\"num\">1.8%</div><div class=\"delta\">▼ 0.3%</div></div>\n        <div class=\"kpi\"><div class=\"label\">NPS</div><div class=\"num\">62</div><div class=\"delta\">▲ 5</div></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"panel\"><h3>Revenue (last 12 weeks)</h3>\n        <div class=\"chart\">\n          <div class=\"bar\" style=\"height:40%\"></div><div class=\"bar\" style=\"height:55%\"></div><div class=\"bar\" style=\"height:48%\"></div>\n          <div class=\"bar\" style=\"height:70%\"></div><div class=\"bar\" style=\"height:62%\"></div><div class=\"bar\" style=\"height:80%\"></div>\n          <div class=\"bar\" style=\"height:75%\"></div><div class=\"bar\" style=\"height:90%\"></div><div class=\"bar\" style=\"height:84%\"></div>\n          <div class=\"bar\" style=\"height:96%\"></div><div class=\"bar\" style=\"height:88%\"></div><div class=\"bar\" style=\"height:100%\"></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"panel\"><h3>Recent orders</h3>\n        <table>\n          <thead><tr><th scope=\"col\">Order</th><th scope=\"col\">Customer</th><th scope=\"col\">Amount</th><th scope=\"col\">Status</th></tr></thead>\n          <tbody>\n            <tr><td>#10241</td><td>Acme Co.</td><td>$1,200</td><td><span class=\"pill ok\">Paid</span></td></tr>\n            <tr><td>#10240</td><td>Globex</td><td>$840</td><td><span class=\"pill pend\">Pending</span></td></tr>\n            <tr><td>#10239</td><td>Initech</td><td>$2,310</td><td><span class=\"pill ok\">Paid</span></td></tr>\n            <tr><td>#10238</td><td>Hooli</td><td>$560</td><td><span class=\"pill ok\">Paid</span></td></tr>\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n      </div>\n    </main>\n  </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
}
